[30;1m633 | [0m[35m-   Kazoo previously would let the same function be registered as a[0m
[30;1m634 | [0m[35m    data-watch or child-watch multiple times, and then call it multiple[0m

[30;1m636 | [0m[35m    behavior, the same watch can now only be registered once for the[0m
